name: What2Drink
0:
”Alexa, run drink options.”
”What should I drink?”
”What else should I drink?”
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: drink options
des: There are a lot of choices when you decide you want to run to the liquor store for libations. What 2 Drink is meant to help you make your decision on what you feel like drinking on any given day.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
